title: ‘Love Is Blind’ Episodes 6-9 Breakdown
description:
Amelia Wedemeyer and Juliet Litman are back to discuss Episodes 6-9 of Netflix’s ‘Love Is Blind’. They examine what reality looks like for each couple as they live together in Chicago, breakdown Shayne and Shaina’s awkward conversation at the cast party, and recap the bachelor and bachelorette parties as everyone looks towards their upcoming nuptials.
Hosts: Amelia Wedemeyer and Juliet Litman
Producers: Devon Manze and Chelsea Stark-Jones
